+From 8c80db40cc0e75ee8d23fb5701cd928c5ef70938 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
+From: "H. Vetinari" <h.vetinari@gmx.com>
+Date: Tue, 27 Jan 2026 16:03:03 +1100
+Subject: [PATCH 10/10] silence pointless error in tf_http_archive
+
